org.jboss.aerogear.sync.client

Class ClientInMemoryDataStore<T,S extends Edit<? extends Diff>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jboss.aerogear.sync.client.ClientInMemoryDataStore<T,S>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The data type data that this implementation can handle.
    S - The type of Edits that this implementation can handle.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ClientDataStore<T,S>, DataStore<T,S>

    public class ClientInMemoryDataStore<T,S extends Edit<? extends Diff>>
extends Object
implements ClientDataStore<T,S>
    An in-memory implementation of ClientDataStore.

    This implementation is mainly intended for testing and example applications.
